                    "soundtoplay": "voice/profx/3_military1_020_020",
                    "text": "%ProfX%: Good job at the Madri Temple. It has been completely disbanded. But I have some bad news. While on a reconnaissance mission of Apocalypse's tower in New York City, Angel was captured. I do not know his fate, but I can only imagine the worst.",
                    "response": {
